dback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Feb 12, 2025</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104vzv1665702534087.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/vzv1665702534087.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/vzv1665702534087.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"vzv1665702534087\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Creates a View of the component instance with the specified name and layout.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"vzv1665702534087__topic_d125585e1_d125586e1_d125587e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vzv1665702534087__p_d125588e1_d125589e1_d125590e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">\n<span class=\"keyword apiname\">uniface.Instance.createView</span>\n</code>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">(</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">ViewName</var>, <var class=\"keyword varname\">ViewLayout</var>, <var class=\"keyword varname\">parentElement</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"vzv1665702534087__section_vdh_n1r_bwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1000639e77\">Arguments</h2>\n<dl class=\"dl parml\" id=\"vzv1665702534087__parml_c1m_v1r_bwb\">\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\">ViewName</dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">A name for the View that is unique within the context of the current server\n                  page.</dd>\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\">ViewLayout</dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">A URL to an HTML layout of the View, or a literal string containing the HTML of\n                  the view layout. </dd>\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\">ParentElement</dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">Makes the view visible in the specified parent element. </dd>\n</dl>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"vzv1665702534087__section_pkw_n1r_bwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1000639e113\">Return Value</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vzv1665702534087__p_d125597e1_d125598e1_d125599e1\">Returns a JavaScript Promise object. If the View is\n            created, the promise is resolved with an instance of <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">uniface.View</span>\n            corresponding to the newly created View.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vzv1665702534087__p_d125600e1_d125601e1_d125602e1\">If creation fails, the promise is rejected with\n            either:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"vzv1665702534087__ul_m1z_bbr_bwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vzv1665702534087__li_d46025e1_d46026e1_d46027e1\">An instance of\n                  <span class=\"keyword apiname\">uniface.DuplicateViewNameException</span> if a View with the specified\n               name already exists. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vzv1665702534087__li_d46028e1_d46029e1_d46030e1\">An instance of <span class=\"keyword apiname\">uniface.Error</span>\n               describing the cause. </li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\">For more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"yqo1665702756208.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yqo1665702756208.html\" title=\"A promise is a placeholder for the return value of an operation that has been called asynchronously. It enables you to specify subsequent actions to be performed with that value when it is eventually received.\">Promises</a>.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"vzv1665702534087__section_g4v_pm5_1dc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1000639e153\">Example: Creating and Addressing Views</h2>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104vzv1665702534087_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"vzv1665702534087__codeblock_spp_hbr_bwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">// creating a view\nmyInstance.createView(\"myView\", \"../myapp/view1.html\", document.getElementById('mydiv')).then(function (view) {\n // view is created and ready\n});\n// getting a view \nvar view = myInstance.getView(\"myview\"); \n// showing a view\nmyInstance.getView(\"myview\").show(\"body\").then(function () {\n // view is now shown and realized\n});</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dtg1665702533539.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>uniface.Instance</a><p>The uniface.Instance object provides access to selected properties and methods of the component instance that it represents.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xbg1665702534713.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>uniface.View</a><p>The uniface.View object represents a view of a component that has been created by calling instance.createView().</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/skz1665702535167.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Multiple Views for Dynamic Server Pages</a><p>A View is an HTML layout that is displayed inside an unbound HTML element in the layout of the web page. Each instance of a dynamic server page (DSP) can have multiple views that provide different layouts for its data.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533257\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533257\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "createView Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Feb 12, 2025 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Creates a View of the component instance with the specified name and layout. uniface.Instance.createView ( ViewName , ViewLayout , parentElement ) Arguments ViewName A name for the View that is unique within the context of the current server page. ViewLayout A URL to an HTML layout of the View, or a literal string containing the HTML of the view layout. ParentElement Makes the view visible in the specified parent element. Return Value Returns a JavaScript Promise object. If the View is created, the promise is resolved with an instance of uniface.View corresponding to the newly created View. If creation fails, the promise is rejected with either: An instance of uniface.DuplicateViewNameException if a View with the specified name already exists. An instance of uniface.Error describing the cause. For more information, see Promises . Example: Creating and Addressing Views Explain this code // creating a view myInstance.createView(\"myView\", \"../myapp/view1.html\", document.getElementById('mydiv')).then(function (view) { // view is created and ready }); // getting a view var view = myInstance.getView(\"myview\"); // showing a view myInstance.getView(\"myview\").show(\"body\").then(function () { // view is now shown and realized }); Copy Related Links uniface.Instance The uniface.Instance object provides access to selected properties and methods of the component instance that it represents. uniface.View The uniface.View object represents a view of a component that has been created by calling instance.createView(). Multiple Views for Dynamic Server Pages A View is an HTML layout that is displayed inside an unbound HTML element in the layout of the web page. Each instance of a dynamic server page (DSP) can have multiple views that provide different layouts for its data. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}